
... Thousands of years ago, you stole into the dungeon of Glok-Yar, intent on
taking the powerful staff within.  Unfortunately, Glok-Yar was still there. 
Enraged at your attempted theft, he bound you to the staff, to serve as its
guardian for all eternity....

CONTROLS:

  Movement:
	7 8 9
	4   6
	1 2 3
 
 ESCAPE:  Quit; exit menu
 ENTER: Ok, confirm (Numeric keypad enter only)
 B: Buy a potion for 250
 A: Apply/use something
 E: Equip
 D: Drop
 U: Unequip
 S: Sell
  
  
